Release Information

Human Anatomy Atlas is our best-selling and
award-winning human anatomy general reference. The
application is a revolutionary 3D visualization and
learning tool used to explore the systems of the
human body. It contains more than 3,600 anatomical
structures, including all major organs and systems
of the male and female body. This application is
used by healthcare professionals, patients
students, and all others interested in detailed
visualization of human anatomy
